function [Y,Xf,Af] = stictionvalue(X,~,~)
%MYNEURALNETWORKFUNCTION neural network simulation function.
%
% Generated by Neural Network Toolbox function genFunction, 06-Mar-2018 16:03:21.
%
% [Y] = myNeuralNetworkFunction(X,~,~) takes these arguments:
